-- Standard Life Investments wins $200 mln equity investment mandate
-- By Simon Jessop
-- Tue Oct 28, 2014 06:30AM EDT
-- None



LONDON, Oct 28 (Reuters) - Standard Life Investments, the fund arm of UK insurer Standard Life <SL.L>, said on Tuesday it had been appointed to run a $200 million equity investment mandate by Denmark-based consultant group Kirstein A/S.

